The territories suffer from many arsons, with the damage at tens of thousands of shekels
In this focus, the "new guard" was established in an attempt to eradicate the difficult phenomenon
(Laughs)
In the documentation that reached "Israel Hayom" you can see grazing areas in the seat of birds that are on fire.
The grasslands are of Zilberman life.
The territories suffer from many arsons, with damage amounting to tens of thousands of shekels.
It should be noted that in this focus the "new guard" was established in an attempt to eradicate the difficult phenomenon.
